      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this absolute gem! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014spotless inside and out, with that perfect 'new car' vibe you've been looking for. It drives like a dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. If you want the best of the best, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
