    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that remains in factory-spec adjustment. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and linear power delivery to the rear wheels. Proactive maintenance has been performed to the highest standard, including reinforced rear subframe mounts and updated rod bearings to ensure long-term structural and internal integrity. The chassis retains its razor-sharp handling characteristics with zero bushing deflection, riding on a perfectly damped suspension setup. Presented in showroom condition with documented service history, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare in the modern market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
