    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car remains in showroom state, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no rock chips or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, retaining that new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and every digital interface remains crisp and responsive. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been maintained strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule at authorized service centers, with a comprehensive binder of records included. It has been exclusively garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seeing inclement weather. This sale includes both original master keys, the complete owner's manual set, and the original window sticker. For the buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
