      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, having been curated with exhaustive attention to detail. Every surface reflects a standard of maintenance rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, this motorcar offers an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite the most discerning enthusiasts to acquire this benchmark of excellence.",
