      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d think she just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it's spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
