      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This specimen represents the zenith of analog engineering, featuring a high-revving, naturally aspirated flat-six coupled to a short-throw six-speed manual gearbox. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, and the compression across all cylinders remains within factory tolerances, ensuring a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of thermal cycling on the exhaust manifolds or fluid seepage from the rear main seal. Handling is razor-sharp thanks to unperished bushings and perfectly calibrated dampers, while the four-piston monobloc calipers provide immense stopping power with zero fade. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and a pristine aesthetic.",
